== Births == * {{ill|Kangen|ja|寛延|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1246]] {{ill|March 26|ja|3月26日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Nikkō Tennō|ja|日興|qq=}}, a monk (died [[1333]])<ref>{{Sfn | 宗旨建立750th year 慶祝記念出版委員会 | 2002 | p = 187 |qq=}}</ref>.
