'''March 8''' is the 8th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March (Lunisolar)|qq=}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Butsumetsu|1=Butsumetsu|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q10886789}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Taiho|en|Taiho|qid=Q423370|lt=Daibō|1=Taiho}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|702|en|702|qid=Q23497|lt=702|1=702}} {{ill|April 9|en|April 9|qid=Q2504|lt=April 9|1=April 9}}) – {{ill|Emperor Monmu|en|Emperor Monmu|qid=Q357246|lt=Bunmu Tennō|1=Emperor Monmu}} established Japan’s first nationally unified system of measurement (度量衡).{{Citation needed|date=2021-02|qq=}}
* {{ill|Hōei|en|Hōei|qid=Q1145262|lt=Hōei|1=Hōei}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1708|en|1708|qid=Q6846|lt=1708|1=1708}} {{ill|April 28|en|April 28|qid=Q2534|lt=April 28|1=April 28}}) – A great fire (the “Hōei no Taika”) broke out in Kyoto, destroying approximately 14,000 houses.
* {{ill|Tenpō|en|Tenpō|qid=Q1369045|lt=Tenpō|1=Tenpō}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1831|en|1831|qid=Q7579|lt=1831|1=1831}} {{ill|April 20|en|April 20|qid=Q2524|lt=April 20|1=April 20}}) – Osaka Machi Bugyō, Shinmi Masaji, dredged the sediment at the mouth of the old Yodogawa (安治川) to build Tenpō-zan.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Kan'en|en|Kan'en|qid=Q1145723|lt=Kangen|1=Kan'en}} 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1246|en|1246|qid=Q5441|lt=1246|1=1246}} {{ill|March 26|en|March 26|qid=Q2456|lt=March 26|1=March 26}}) – {{ill|Nikkō Shōnin|en|Nikkō Shōnin|qid=Q373169|lt=Nikkō Tennō|1=Nikkō Shōnin}}, a monk (died {{ill|1333|en|1333|qid=Q6004|lt=1333|1=1333}})<ref>{{Sfn | 宗旨建立750th year 慶祝記念出版委員会 | 2002 | p = 187 |qq=}}</ref>.

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Ansei|en|Ansei|qid=Q1327259|lt=Ansei|1=Ansei}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1858|en|1858|qid=Q7684|lt=1858|1=1858}} {{ill|April 20|en|April 20|qid=Q2524|lt=April 20|1=April 20}}) – {{ill|Ōhara Yūgaku|en|Ōhara Yūgaku|qid=Q11433147|lt=Ōhara Yūgaku|1=Ōhara Yūgaku}}, an agricultural scholar (born {{ill|1797|en|1797|qid=Q7820|lt=1797|1=1797}}).

